Body: There is no airdrop, we actually announced this many times previously. Title: ðŸ“ŒðŸ“Œ[ANN] [GUESS] Peerguess - Collaborative Cryptocurrency TickerðŸ“ŒðŸ“Œ ICO 28 OCTOBER
Body: Hello Dear Peerguess Community,  We want to inform you about token listing. As you know GUESS token was listed on Yobit last week. The trade of GUESS token is active there. You can reach GUESS market on Yobit by following the link below:  https://yobit.net/en/trade/GUESS/BTC  We also would like to announce that GUESS token is listed on IDEX and Token.Store exchanges as well. You can reach GUESS markets by following the links below.  https://idex.market/eth/guess  https://token.store/trade/GUESS  Peerguess team has also been working to make agreement with more exchanges. Bigger excahnge platforms will come eventually, but this won't happen immediately. It's a progress just like our app development. We can assure you that official team never stops working on token listing.  Now, it's time to focus a bit more on our app release on iOS platform. Our priority is now iOS release of peerguess application. Rather than ICOs selling only their raw ideas, we come up with a working platform which is under development for couple of months.  As of now, we released peerguess app on four different countries consists of Turkey, Denmark, Philippines and Thailand. Before a global release, we need some feedback and testimonials.  If you're interested in downloading peerguess app, you can change your app store region to one of those counted. This way, you'll be able to download and test it! If you're registered in one of those four countries, please download and use our application. We need your comments. We're receving feedbacks from the active users and we're now preparing for the global release of peerguess app on Ä°OS platform.  For the questions about Android release of peerguess app, we can say that after our global release on iOS, we will work harder on Android development. Stay tuned with peerguess project and don't hesitate to ask your questions to us. We'll gladly help you!  Best Regards, Peerguess Team  Also read from our official Twitter account: https://twitter.com/peerguess/status/955220098020728832

Body: Dear peerguess investors and followers,  We would like to clarify the current state of GUESS token distribution process.As many of you know, we were planning to distribute the tokens within Dec 9th to 16th period, but as we are still waiting to be listed on the exchanges, we postponed the distribution of the tokens to protect our investors.  For now, we created our token, got acceptance from etherscan, distributed private pre-ico tokens for testing purposes and stopped it. We believe that we will be listed on EtherDelta and Yobit next week. And after the market is stabilized, we will start distributing the tokens of pre-ICO, ICO and bounty participants, in order.  Please bear in mind that we are always here and we will be in touch with you in every step of our phases. Donâ€™t hesitate to reach us via our official channels when you have questions.  https://twitter.com/peerguess/status/942513372452610048  Regards, Peerguess Team

Recommendation Engine (RE) will: â€º Display a list of cryptocurrencies for users who predict both a cryptocurrency and another currency (like e-commerce recommendations). â€º Recommend currencies based on your prediction history and your segmentation.  Auto-Trade (AT) will use the historical success rates and many other indicators to create triggers and parameters from the application and make trades on your chosen exchange/platform1  Stigmergic Quantitative Data (SQD) will be based on Positive and Negative Guesses made, which can be filtered by Country, Time Zone, Language and many more data fields to assist you to understand the different dynamics on cryptocurrency world.

Author: xsentus
Title: ðŸ“ŒðŸ“Œ[ANN] [GUESS] Peerguess - Collaborative Cryptocurrency TickerðŸ“ŒðŸ“Œ ICO 28 OCTOBER
Body: Hello,  Although our project resembles both, the main difference is guessing is not our application's primary feature. We are providing all-in-one bitcoin/altcoin price ticker, portfolio mng, alert mng to all (not just ico) users. Therefore we will have a huge userbase. And in parallel (using gamification techniques) we will push our users to spend gems and make guesses.  In real life, election polls are gathered from less than 0.01% of the population; and individuals participating the survey are just declaring their intention, yet many of the election polls publishing the correct (or near correct) results weeks before the election. Thus, you are right for one individual or a small group of individuals, guessing is just a representation of intention or sentiment but if you closely look to our White Paper, you will see that when the group of guessers increases, the chance to reach a correct output highly increases. Condorcet Jury Theorem and many more clearly state that.  Best, Peerguess Team

Author: xsentus
Title: ðŸ“ŒðŸ“Œ[ANN] [GUESS] Peerguess - Collaborative Cryptocurrency TickerðŸ“ŒðŸ“Œ ICO 28 OCTOBER
Body: Exactly. Our main game plan is to be the number one cryptocurrency ticker in the world, and to do this we will be attacking on every group of user on IOS, Android, Tablets, Smartwatches. Second, if we can raise enough money on the ICO we will be providing FX tickers and ability to set guesses with cross worlds; for example you would be able to create a coupon guess of bitcoin will fall + usd/aud will raise with different parity.  Therefore in the mid term, we plan to attract the FX world users too and have a huge user base. As we also believe people will find addictive to play and win, both crypto and real-money world users will need to buy GUESS tokens to convert to gems or people will convert their winnings in gems to tokens. This is also the reason why we keep a liquidation reserve.  Also keep in mind that every Sunday morning, we will distribute 100 Gems to all holders of the GUESS tokens for each 10,000 GUESS tokens they kept for 7 days. For example, a token holder with 25,000 GUESS tokens will receive 250 free Gems on Sunday morning. This will also create demand for GUESS tokens on its own.
